{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s001", "order": 1, "text": "**Feature Requirement Document: Destructive Intent Confirmation**", "char_start": 0, "char_end": 65, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 9}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s002", "order": 2, "text": "**Feature Name:** Destructive Intent Voice Confirmation and Safety Logging", "char_start": 67, "char_end": 141, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 11}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s003", "order": 3, "text": "**Objective:**", "char_start": 143, "char_end": 157, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 3}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s004", "order": 4, "text": "To ensure user safety and prevent accidental data loss, a confirmation mechanism must be added when the detected user intent is classified as destructive, specifically when it matches the \"delete everything\" command.", "char_start": 160, "char_end": 376, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 37}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s005", "order": 5, "text": "**Requirements:**", "char_start": 378, "char_end": 395, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 3}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s006", "order": 6, "text": "1. **Intent Validation:**  \n   - Trigger confirmation flow only if the detected intent equals \"delete everything\".  \n   -", "char_start": 397, "char_end": 518, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 21}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s007", "order": 7, "text": "The detected intent must have a confidence score of **≥ 0.9** to proceed.", "char_start": 519, "char_end": 592, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 14}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s008", "order": 8, "text": "2. **User Confirmation:**  \n   - A verbal confirmation must be requested.  \n   -", "char_start": 594, "char_end": 674, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 14}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s009", "order": 9, "text": "The system must explicitly ask: *“Are you sure you want to delete everything?”*  \n   - The user must respond with an exact verbal **“yes”** to proceed.", "char_start": 675, "char_end": 826, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 36}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s010", "order": 10, "text": "Any other response cancels the action.", "char_start": 827, "char_end": 865, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 7}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s011", "order": 11, "text": "3. **Event Logging:**  \n   - All such destructive intent actions must be logged to the `voice_safety` index.  \n   -", "char_start": 867, "char_end": 982, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 22}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s012", "order": 12, "text": "The log must include timestamp, user ID, intent string, confidence score, and confirmation response.", "char_start": 983, "char_end": 1083, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 19}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s013", "order": 13, "text": "4. **Rollback Capability:**  \n   - A rollback option must be available for **10 minutes** post-execution.", "char_start": 1085, "char_end": 1190, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 21}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s014", "order": 14, "text": "- Rollback must reverse the “delete everything” operation entirely if invoked within the allowed window.", "char_start": 1196, "char_end": 1300, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 18}
{"doc_id": "bb77b3b2-e255-58ac-aeb9-796c8fd14503", "req_id": "REQ-150", "sent_id": "REQ-150::s015", "order": 15, "text": "**Priority:** High  \n**Owner:** Voice Interaction Safety Team", "char_start": 1302, "char_end": 1363, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 11}
